it is between 0=C2=B0 and 180=C2=B0),</li><li>=E2=80=96<b>a</b>=E2=80=96 an=
d =E2=80=96<b>b</b>=E2=80=96 are the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wi=
ki/Magnitude_(vector)" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Magnitude (vector)">m=
agnitudes</a> of vectors <b>a</b> and <b>b</b>,</li><li><b>n</b> is a <a hr=
