lass=3D"nowrap"><i>=CE=B8</i> =3D 180=C2=B0</span> and <span class=3D"nowra=
p">sin&nbsp;<i>=CE=B8</i> =3D 0</span>).
</p><p>The self cross product of a vector is the zero vector:
