<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Lagrange's_identity"><span =
id=3D"Lagrange.27s_identity"></span>Lagrange's identity</h3><span class=3D"=
mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"h=
ttps://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DCross_product&amp;action=3Dedit=
&amp;section=3D15" title=3D"Edit section: Lagrange's identity"><span>edit</=
span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>The relation
<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=3D"mwe-=
