isplaystyle \left\|\mathbf {a} \times \mathbf {b} \right\|^{2}\equiv \det {=
\begin{bmatrix}\mathbf {a} \cdot \mathbf {a} &amp;\mathbf {a} \cdot \mathbf=
 {b} \\\mathbf {a} \cdot \mathbf {b} &amp;\mathbf {b} \cdot \mathbf {b} \en=
d{bmatrix}}\equiv \left\|\mathbf {a} \right\|^{2}\left\|\mathbf {b} \right\=
|^{2}-(\mathbf {a} \cdot \mathbf {b} )^{2}}">
