 Cross visualization"><span>edit</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-br=
acket">]</span></span></div>
<p>Similarly to the mnemonic device above, a "cross" or X can be visualized=
 between the two vectors in the equation. This may be helpful for rememberi=
ng the correct cross product formula.
</p><p>If
</p><p><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=
=3D"mwe-math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;">=
<math display=3D"block" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttex=
t=3D"{\displaystyle \mathbf {a} =3D\mathbf {b} \times \mathbf {c} }">
