</p>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Lorentz_force">Lorentz forc=
e</h3><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket"=
>[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DCross_prod=
uct&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D26" title=3D"Edit section: Lorentz forc=
e"><span>edit</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></sp=
an></div>
<link rel=3D"mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href=3D"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r=
1320445320"><div role=3D"note" class=3D"hatnote navigation-not-searchable">=
See also: <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lorentz_force" title=3D"=
Lorentz force">Lorentz force</a></div>
<p>The cross product is used to describe the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedi=
a.org/wiki/Lorentz_force" title=3D"Lorentz force">Lorentz force</a> experie=
nced by a moving electric charge <span class=3D"nowrap"><span class=3D"texh=
tml"><i>q<sub>e</sub></i></span>:</span>
<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-block"><span class=3D"mwe-=
math-mathml-display mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math di=
splay=3D"block" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\d=
isplaystyle \mathbf {F} =3Dq_{e}\left(\mathbf {E} +\mathbf {v} \times \math=
bf {B} \right)}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
