            <mn>3</mn>
          </mrow>
        </msup>
        <mo>.</mo>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle \mathbf {R} ^=
{3}.}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/621a5f78791e33a0d47e7e344046f77523425d9f" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.338ex; width:3.704ex; height:2.676ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle \ma=
thbf {R} ^{3}.}"></span> In the basis <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-m=
